OL,3,C'I don't live, I exist': Jersey
OL,4,Cresidents on cost of living pressures
OL,6,FJersey residents say they are
OL,7,Fstruggling to make ends meet and
OL,8,Ffacing financial ruin because of the
OL,9,Frising cost of living.
OL,11,FLatest figures published by Policy
OL,12,FCentre Jersey reveal that islanders
OL,13,Fare paying up to 49% more for their
OL,14,Fweekly shop compared to the UK.
OL,16,FJane says: "The cost of living is
OL,17,Fcrippling, I am a Jersey person born
OL,18,Fand bred, and I get #47.50 a week to
OL,19,Flive on. Well, I don't live, I exist.
