OL,3,C'I don't live, I exist': Jersey
OL,4,Cresidents on cost of living pressures
OL,6,F"I have worked all my life, and all I
OL,7,Fget is my pension. I live out of my
OL,8,Foverdraft. It is ridiculous."
OL,10,FShe says the pressure of constantly
OL,11,Ftrying to make ends meet has taken its
OL,12,Ftoll.
OL,14,FJane explains: "Well, put it this way,
OL,15,Flast Christmas I had to fight so hard
OL,16,Fnot to take my own life, and I mean
OL,17,Fthat - I really was in a very, very
OL,18,Fdark place.
