OL,4,Cresidents on cost of living pressures
OL,6,F"I was sitting with a microwave
OL,7,Fdinner, on my own, I haven't got a
OL,8,Fcooker, I have a microwave and an
OL,9,Fairfryer, and if it doesn't go in
OL,10,Feither of them, then I don't eat.
OL,12,F"You shop for the cheapest food, which
OL,13,Fis the worst food going, but the cost
OL,14,Fof living here is outrageous."
OL,16,FData from Policy Centre Jersey shows:
