OL,3,C'I don't live, I exist': Jersey
OL,4,Cresidents on cost of living pressures
OL,6,FHowever, in 2020 and 2021, the report
OL,7,Fexplains that average household income
OL,8,Fbefore housing costs in Jersey was 51%
OL,9,Fhigher than in the UK, and 42% higher
OL,10,Fafter housing costs.
OL,12,FIslanders facing financial
OL,13,Fdifficulties included 82% of single
OL,14,Fparents, 47% of couples with children,
OL,15,F36% of working-age individuals living
OL,16,Falone, and 24% of pensioners.
OL,18,FThe independent think tank warns that
OL,19,Fif the high cost of living is not
OL,20,Faddressed, more people will leave the
OL,21,Fisland.
