OL,3,C'I don't live, I exist': Jersey
OL,4,Cresidents on cost of living pressures
OL,6,FSir Mark Boleat, Senior Advisor at
OL,7,FPolicy Centre Jersey, says: "It means
OL,8,Fthe island is struggling to keep
OL,9,Fpeople born and brought up here, in
OL,10,FJersey. People are leaving to find
OL,11,Fsomewhere they can afford to live.
OL,13,F"And then it's difficult to bring in
OL,14,Fthe people we need. Whether it's
OL,15,Feducation, health or finance
OL,16,Findustries.
OL,18,F"We need to bring in people because
OL,19,Fnot all the skills are available on
OL,20,Fthe island."
