OL,6,FJersey's Minister for Sustainable
OL,7,FEconomic Development says increasing
OL,8,Fthe supply of housing is key to
OL,9,Freducing its cost.
OL,11,FDeputy Morel says: "We have made it
OL,12,Fdifficult for ourselves as the States
OL,13,Fof Jersey to increase supply. I've
OL,14,Fbeen a part of that. Every other
OL,15,FState's Member has been a part of
OL,16,Fthat."
