OL,3,C'I don't live, I exist': Jersey
OL,4,Cresidents on cost of living pressures
OL,6,FJersey resident John shares how the
OL,7,Fcosts have been challenging, he
OL,8,Fexplains: "It's tight, my wife wasn't
OL,9,Fwell, and I have been looking out for
OL,10,Fher. She had been in a nursing home,
OL,11,Fwe had to make do the best we could
OL,12,Fbecause whilst she was there, it was
OL,13,Fcosting us a fortune. We are literally
OL,14,Fdown to our basics now, but we
OL,15,Fpersevere."
OL,17,FAnother shopper told ITV News he is
OL,18,Fretired, but says he had to take on a
OL,19,Fpart-time role amid the rising costs.
