OL,3,C'I don't live, I exist': Jersey
OL,4,Cresidents on cost of living pressures
OL,6,FHe explains: "I do takeaway delivery
OL,7,Fon a night-time just to earn some
OL,8,Fmoney, that's how I afford to go away,
OL,9,Fotherwise I wouldn't be able to, I
OL,10,Fwouldn't be able to afford it."
OL,12,FHe adds he goes to England to do some
OL,13,Fof his shopping and fill up his car,
OL,14,Fas it is still cheaper than on island.
