OL,6,FAlice Nun from the Salvation Army
OL,7,Fsays: "Although Covid was super busy,
OL,8,Fit feels like we are at similar levels
OL,9,Fagain. We have only had this shop open
OL,10,Ffor the last three and a half months,
OL,11,Fbut we have already got more than 400
OL,12,Ffamilies.
OL,14,F"People are choosing to keep a roof
OL,15,Fover their head and pay their rent,
OL,16,Fthen sometimes picking food."
