OL,3,C'I don't live, I exist': Jersey
OL,4,Cresidents on cost of living pressures
OL,6,FThere is a similar picture in
OL,7,FGuernsey, as the island's Community
OL,8,FFoundation's report, published in May,
OL,9,Fhighlighted that 38% of the island's
OL,10,Fpoorest households do not have enough
OL,11,Fbeds for the number of people living
OL,12,Fthere.
OL,14,FThe first report of its kind for the
OL,15,Fisland included data from one of the
OL,16,Flargest surveys ever conducted
OL,17,Flocally, with 3,000 islanders taking
OL,18,Fpart.
