OL,7,Fsays: "I always try to do my best to
OL,8,Fmake sure the children are clothed,
OL,9,Fhave been fed, have electric, heating,
OL,10,Fwhich means that sometimes I don't
OL,11,Fnecessarily get to do X, Y and Z or
OL,12,Fsometimes I will go without having
OL,13,Fcertain meals I want to make sure that
OL,14,Fmy kids have eaten and that's that."
